@startuml icy-state-machine
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false

title IcyParser State Machine

[*] --> WAIT_AUDIO

WAIT_AUDIO --> READ_META_LEN : metaint bytes consumed\n(emit AudioChunk)
READ_META_LEN --> READ_META : 1 byte read (meta_len)
READ_META --> WAIT_AUDIO : meta_len bytes consumed\n(parse StreamTitle)\n(emit TitleChanged if changed)

note right of WAIT_AUDIO : Default state.\nAccumulates audio bytes\nuntil icy-metaint reached.
note right of READ_META_LEN : Reads 1 byte = length\nof next metadata block\n(0 = no metadata this cycle)
note right of READ_META : Reads meta_len bytes.\nParses StreamTitle='...';\nIf title changed → TitleChanged

WAIT_AUDIO --> [*] : stop
@enduml